3.
Nested conditionals is when one conditional is nested inside another conditional.
Example code:
if(x < y)
{
    print("x is less than y");
}
else
{
    if (x > y)                                   //nested conditional
        print("x is greater than y");
    else
        print("x and y must be equal");
}